{id:"spell-knock",name:"Knock",content:[{id:"Title",content:"Knock"},{id:"StatGrid",content:[{title:"Level",content:"2"},{title:"Casting Time",content:"1 action"},{title:"Range",content:"60 feet"},{title:"Components",content:"V"},{title:"Duration",content:"Instantaneous"},{title:"School",content:"Transmutation"}]},{id:"Subtitle",content:"Effect"},{id:"MultiText",content:["Choose an object that you can see within range. The object can be a door, a box, a chest, a set of manacles, a padlock, or another object that contains a mundane or magical means that prevents access.","A target that is held shut by a mundane lock or that is stuck or barred becomes unlocked, unstuck, or unbarred. If the object has multiple locks, only one of them is unlocked.","If you choose a target that is held shut with arcane lock, that spell is suppressed for 10 minutes, during which time the target can be opened and shut normally.","When you cast the spell, a loud knock, audible from as far away as 300 feet, emanates from the target object."]}]}